---
title: Brioche Lemon Sugar French Toast with Honey-Baked Fruit & Cherry Sauce | Serves 2
description: Skip the café queue and add some sweetness to brunch time with our brioche lemon sugar French toast. Stack it high with cherry
sauce and honey-baked fruit, then top with whipped cream for a decadent dish worth savouring.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/brunch-nz-lemon-sugar-french-toasted-brioche-1d1cb1ac.jpg
